Class ParticipantImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fraunhofer.iais.eis.ParticipantImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Agent, Described, ManagedEntity, ModelClass, Participant
    public class ParticipantImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements Participant
    Default implementation of package de.fraunhofer.iais.eis.Participant Stakeholder in the International Data Spaces, assuming one or more of the predefined roles; every participant is given a unique identity by the Identity Provider.
